ZZ - MLB - HOMERUN DERBY TRACKER (2017) - OBSOLETE
description:
WIKI: https://wiki.mlbam.com/display/proddev/Home+Run+Derby+Tracker+2017

EPIC: https://jira.mlbam.com/browse/JSGD-1845

JIRA: https://jira.mlbam.com/browse/JSGD-2229
-8 players are seeded and compete for the title over the course of 3 rounds.
--In each round players are paired off and go head to head.

-In every round each player gets to swing at as many pitches as possible over the course of 4 minutes.
--During those 4 minutes, if a player hits two home runs measured at 440 feet or more, he will be rewarded with 30 seconds of extra time for that round.
--Only one time bonus will be awarded per player per round.

-Time-outs.
--Each player gets a single 45 second time-out in rounds 1 and 2.
--Each player gets two 45 second time-outs in the final round.

-If there is a tie in any round, the batters engage in a swing-off, during which time they try to hit as many home runs as possible in 1 minute.
--No bonus time is awarded in a swing-off.
--If there is still a tie, each player swings at 3 pitches.
--If a tie still exists, it goes to sudden death.

2017 SEEDS
1. Giancarlo Stanton
2. Aaron Judge
3. Cody Bellinger
4. Mike Moustakas
5. Miguel Sano
6. Charlie Blackmon
7. Justin Bour
8. Gary Sanchez

BRACKET
1 vs. 8
2 vs. 7
4 vs. 5
3 vs. 6

name: Brackets [Web]
description:
https://baseball.atlassian.net/browse/MLBWEB-356


Error Submit
Prerequisite:
bracket must be inactive (e.g. - '/es/brackets/food-fight-2021')
expected notification: 'Something went wrong when submitting your bracket.'

Everything else below this line can be tested at:

https://beta-gcp.mlb.com/es/brackets/home-run-derby-2022 

Error Submit Underage
expected notification: 'Sorry! You are not eligible to play this bracket.'

Error First And Last Name
expected notification: 'Please provide your first and last name'

Error Tiebreakers
expected notification: 'Please answer all required questions *'

Error Invalid Date Of Birth
expected notification: 'Please enter a valid Date of Birth'

Info Login
expected notification: 'Log In to your MLB account to view your bracket entry'

Submit Success
expected notification: 'Bracket has been submitted successfully.'

Info Bracket Reset
Prerequisite:
Logged in
Has submitted bracket previously

arrive to page

expected notification: 'Previous bracket submission found and all picks are updated to previously submitted state.'

Error Submit Locked
Prerequisite:
Bracket config > App State: live
Bracket config > Bracket State: open

fill out bracket

click submit

fill out all fields appropriately

go to Contentful and update Bracket config:
 a. App State: live
 b. Bracket State: locked

go back to bracket and click submit

log in

fill out all fields appropriately

expected notification: 'Bracket submission failed as bracket is in locked state.'

Info Locked
Prerequisite:
Bracket config > App State: post
Bracket config > Bracket State: locked

arrive to page

expected notification: 'The bracket contest is now locked. Check back soon to see the results!'
